2011-10-04 Stefan Kesselheim <stefan@kesselheim-online.de>

 * src/particle_data.c: Bugfix 33489 ( setting dip and quat simultanously)
 part dip and part quat can not be set in the same command also: part dip and
 part dipm can not be set in the same command  Both cases could lead to
 ambigous results.

 * testsuite/lb.tcl: changed the necessary precision in the lb testcase

