2010-09-03 Stefan Kesselheim <Stefan.Kesselheim@icp.uni-stuttgart.de>

 * lb-boundaries.h, lb.c, lb.h: additions and correction

2010-08-26 Stefan Kesselheim <Stefan.Kesselheim@icp.uni-stuttgart.de>

 * lb-boundaries.c, lb-boundaries.h, lb.c: We realized that we have a slip,
 depending on the orientation of the LB wall and the LB cell length.

2010-08-25 Stefan Kesselheim <Stefan.Kesselheim@icp.uni-stuttgart.de>

 * lb.c, lb.h: fixed conversion factor for external forces in LB

2010-08-18 Stefan Kesselheim <Stefan.Kesselheim@icp.uni-stuttgart.de>

 * lb-boundaries.c, lb.h: lb_boundary wall, sphere, cylinder work

 * lb.c, lb.h: changes work in progress

 * communication.c, lb-boundaries.h: added some functionality for
 lb-boundaries

 * lb-boundaries.c: Implemented "lb_boundary sphere" command

2010-08-17 Stefan Kesselheim <Stefan.Kesselheim@icp.uni-stuttgart.de>

 * communication.c, communication.h, lb-boundaries.c, lb.c, lb.h: TCL command
 "lbnode x y z print boundary" works.

2010-08-16 Stefan Kesselheim <Stefan.Kesselheim@icp.uni-stuttgart.de>

 * initialize.c, lb-boundaries.c, lb.c, lb.h: Couldn't make up a test routine
 for the placement of the wall that quickly. Discovered that the bounce-back
 part at the walls doesn't work as intended.

2010-08-04 Stefan Kesselheim <Stefan.Kesselheim@icp.uni-stuttgart.de>

 * initialize.c, lb-boundaries.c, lb.c: added a few functionalities, mainly
 lbnode command

 * communication.c, communication.h, initialize.c, lattice.h, lb-boundaries.c,
 lb-boundaries.h, lb.c, lb.h: Lattice-Boltzmann arbitrary wall boundary works
 and marks fluid nodes correctly.

2010-07-19 Stefan Kesselheim <Stefan.Kesselheim@icp.uni-stuttgart.de>

 * communication.c, communication.h, initialize.c, initialize.h,
 lb-boundaries.c, lb-boundaries.h, lb.h: Half merged version (version before
 branching + Ulis LB version + 2 new lb-boundary.c/.h from Stefan). Not
 functional, only for Stefan.

 * lattice.h: *** empty log message ***

 * communication.c, config.c, halo.c, halo.h, initialize.c, integrate.c,
 lattice.c, lattice.h, lb-boundaries.c, lb-boundaries.h, lb-d3q19.h, random.h,
 statistics_fluid.c, statistics_fluid.h, thermostat.c: some more added
 features, homogenized stuff and so on.

2010-10-14  Olaf Lenz  <olenz@icp.uni-stuttgart.de>

 * Started ChangeLog. For older changes, see ./old/RELEASE_NOTES.
